body: This version fixes the bug reported in #243

body: Due to its annoying bug `RedundantThrows` check was disabled

name: More checks
body: This version adds more checks to the package, and fixes some old bugs.

name: Two new plugins
body: `maven-duplicate-finder-plugin` and `jslint-maven-plugin` added to the list of checks. Besides that, a few bugs fixed

name: New Checkstyle and PMD checks
body: This version upgraded PMD to 5.1 and introduced a few new Checkstyle checks. Try it out!

name: Bug fixes
body: Minor bug fix, that makes this version stable

name: Checkstyle checks
body: This versions adds a few new Checkstyle checks.

name: Better formatting of exclusions
body:
In this version every exclusion should start with a prefix, for example:

```
checkstyle:/src/it/.*
findbugs:.*
```

etc.

name: FindBugs and exclusions in Maven plugin
body: This version enables FindBugs, which was disabled long time ago. Besides that, it adds a configuration parameter to qulice-maven-plugin, to enable exclusions of entire blocks/files: http://www.qulice.com/qulice-maven-plugin/example-exclude.html

name: Stricter rules
body: This version adds more Checkstyle and PMD rules.

name: Bug fix in Checkstyle
body: This version fixes an annoying bug #41

name: Maven 3.0 and 3.1 compatibility
body: This release makes `qulice-maven-plugin` compatible with Maven 3.0 and 3.1 at the same time.
